{"tid":840270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"前度含淚提出分手 復合有冇機","createTime":"2018-09-28T15:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T17:50:57.000Z","uid":205073,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"472040b32cf36c08aa2652083747f90f644ad052","tid":840270,"uid":205073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"本來一齊就嚟兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中秋嗰時仲訓係同一張床<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係中秋紅日我係仆街我係垃圾搞到有少少爭執<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰日返到家我好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住聽日接佢放工道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後見到佢snap全晚都冇返過屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n凌晨四點whatsapp提出分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話佢自卑（因為我而家讀緊大學同佢讀緊asso 雖然我覺得一啲都唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）同埋當我係妹 似湊女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我崩潰咗成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚見佢商討嗰陣我話我會學識獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都諗通咗繼續同佢一齊只會依賴佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我話我唔會留佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我都想解決而家嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話佢點都要做一次衰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係我唔會大個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後錫咗淡攬咗吓就應承咗佢分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家仲有keep contact仲係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我內心都係sad到仆街 好唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家鬧我仆街臭雞話我抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係認真問男人感情過咗幾耐會淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時復合最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我而家已經嘗試獨立啲照顧好自己保護好自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我仲有冇其他辦法可以令佢回心轉意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770244a0068147bbbadf22d4c4f245e224004f17","tid":840270,"uid":207522,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一炮解千愁"},{"pid":"0539e30e93fc0f509bd8f95c370473e24021338a","tid":840270,"uid":828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"喜極而泣"},{"pid":"07b75c28b20810cb4a594233001169a931194580","tid":840270,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80369f53da823a91047ece87499f121b13003802","t