T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"對唔住係我錯我係臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩補救方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a059042e72cb19b45056dfb3d359f1ed1eff17","tid":840270,"uid":205073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇多啲人答吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f41766ac6f1f55aedd3fcd92d3e2b3dcf8ea371","tid":840270,"uid":99086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"明知條仔咁撚自卑仲講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6220cad1e67d392eb8127570745cf91068b549","tid":840270,"uid":114035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"男人最忌比人話唔得 你篤中佢死穴"},{"pid":"8894bef43d366483feba1a9ec04428418ee11517","tid":840270,"uid":19852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf93f7ae0390103b0a14856a99c6df106e8aa2b","tid":840270,"uid":205073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f41766ac6f1f55aedd3fcd92d3e2b3dcf8ea371","tid":840270,"uid":99086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"明知條仔咁撚自卑仲講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"我嗰時個腦唔知去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a